{"word":"G5350 - φθέγγομαι - phthéngomai - ftheng'-gom-ahee - Speak","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">φθέγγομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">phthéngomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ftheng'-gom-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Speak</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பேசு"},{"paragraph":"1. to give out a sound, noise, or cry"},{"paragraph":"2. to proclaim; to speak, utter"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably akin to <a href=\"#/G5338 - φέγγος - phéngos - feng'-gos/5338\">G5338</a> and thus to <a href=\"#/G5346 - φημί - phēmí - fay-mee'/5346\">G5346</a>; to <i>utter</i> a clear sound, that is, (genitive case) to <i>proclaim:</i> - speak.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}